  {
    "title": "Lore",
    "depth": 1,
    "paragraphs": [
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "Natalia was orphaned from the war and she was raised as a little girl by the Monastery of Light.",
            "links": [
              {
                "type": "internal",
                "page": "Monastery of Light"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": "Natalia was trained into becoming one of the Light assassins."
          },
          {
            "text": "This young phenom had risen to become the top assassin for the Monastery, via her outstanding talents."
          },
          {
            "text": "However, on one assassination mission, she failed in her execution, causing her companions to meet with unprecedented disaster and death."
          },
          {
            "text": "Although she managed to escape danger, with Tigreal's help, this was undoubtedly a severe blow to Natalia's pride.",
            "links": [
              {
                "type": "internal",
                "page": "Tigreal"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": "To prove herself again, she exiled herself to the outskirts of the land, far from the Moniyan Empire and the Monastery of Light, to carry out more dangerous missions.",
            "links": [
              {
                "type": "internal",
                "page": "Moniyan Empire"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": "It is never known who her target is or where she might strike next."
          },
          {
            "text": "All that people know is that Natalia intends to win back all that she once possessed."
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "templates": [
      {
        "template": "clr"
      }
    ]
  },
