    "templates": [
      {
        "list": [
          "Miya"
        ],
        "template": "hi"
      }
    ],
    "lists": [
      [
        {
          "text": "Natalia's name has Latin origins and means \"Christmas Day;\" the name was usually given to girls born in Christmas period. Coincidentally, she was released on the month of December 2016."
        },
        {
          "text": "Natalia is likely inspired by the Assassins of the Assassin's Creed video game series as evident on her design and quotes.",
          "links": [
            {
              "text": "''Assassin's Creed'' video game series",
              "type": "interwiki",
              "wiki": "wikipedia",
              "page": "Assassin's Creed"
            }
          ],
          "formatting": {
            "italic": [
              "Assassin's Creed"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "text": "Natalia is one of the heroes who has an ability that interacts with the environment (the bush)."
        },
        {
          "text": "Her ultimate quote ultimate quote, \"Nothing is true!\", is a phrase attributed to Hassan-i Sabbah, the founder of Order of the Hashshashin from which the term \"assassin\" originates."
        },
        {
          "text": "Cyber Spectre is the skin of Best Design in MLBB 1st Skin Design Competition by MGL."
        },
        {
          "text": "Natalia's Collector Skin \"Warrioress Paragon\" was given away for a limited-time, Making it the first free collector skin ever."
        },
        {
          "text": "Natalia free collector skin and Miiya collector skin are related. 's arrows can open portals to the future. Natalia came through this portal."
        }
      ]
    ]
  }
